Introduction

AWEEK was a seven-member boy group formed by Illusion Entertainment and Oneworld Entertainment. The group initially had six members and had pre-debut activities in Japan in 2018. They made their official debut on January 31, 2019, with the digital single “The More I See”.

On December 31, 2022, as per the Instagram posts of Logan and Di1e, AWEEK has officially disbanded.
